commit.message:
pre5.2.3: Updated autoconf/config.guess, autoconf/config.sub, doc/tm/most.tm
and regenerated most.txt and most.1 (based on patches from Basil
Feitknecht to address 3, 5, 13, 14 and pull request 22)
pre5.2.2: Added a few typecasts to suppress warnings when compiled against slang v3 which uses const and void in its API
pre5.2.1: Updates to support windows console
Version 5.2.0 release
pre5.2.0-13: Better support for 256 color terminals; added additional test file
pre5.2.0-12: Updated the copyright year
pre5.2.0-11: An unspecifed FG or BG color was not getting properly mapped to the default color
pre5.2.0-10: Support color escape sequences that use the colon character as a delimiter
pre5.2.0-9: Fixed a bug that prevented the character following a 0 width character not to be displayed.
pre5.2-8: Added pseudo-truecolor support for terminals that provide only the basic 16 colors by mapping the desired truecolor to the nearest 16 color version.
pre5.2-7: Added support for true-color terminals.  See changes.txt for additional information.
pre5.2-6: src/Makefile.in: Avoid a race condition when performing a parallel build
pre5.2-5: Additional changes involving int -> MOST_INT were required
pre5.2-4: Fixed some issues with files larger than 4 GB.
pre5.2-3: Add support for the embedded default forground/background escape sequences
pre5.2-2: Changed a /* drop */ comment to /* fall through */ to avoid a gcc warning
pre5.2-1:  Ignore empty filenames on the command line
Version 5.1.0 released
pre5.1-25: Updated manifest and copyrights updated for 2019 release
pre5.1-24: Updated docs and copyrights for upcoming release
pre5.1-23: Added LDFLAGS to chkslang linker line
pre5.1-22: Updated configure to use aclocal.m4 v0.3.3-1
pre5.1-21: Added a work-around for programs that try colorize the output using the clear-to-end-of-line escape sequence (ESC[K) without regard for the value of isatty(fileno(sdout)).
pre5.1-20: Added support for Home/End keys
pre5.1-18: Added regexp search support
pre5.1-17 Updated copyright year
pre5.1 change 17:  Fixed an issue with the display of double-width characters to address <https://bugs.launchpad.net/ubuntu/+source/most/+bug/312454>.
pre5.1 change 16: updated autoconf scripts
pre5.1 change 15: Use /etc/ld.so.conf to located system lib paths.
pre5.1 change 14: Removed some unused variables
